news.title: Existing home sales in U.S. drop 5.9% in October 2022
news.para: House resales, which account for a big chunk of U.S. home sales, slumped 28.4% on a year-on-year basis in October. That was the largest drop since February 2008.

news.title: NCLAT stays insolvency proceedings against BPTP
news.para: ​On November 14, the National Company Law Tribunal (NCLT) had directed to initiate insolvency proceedings against BPTP Ltd, a leading real estate player in Delhi-NCR, on a petition filed by an operational creditor, RBCL Projects.

news.title: Delhi: Metropolis Lab's MD buys Sunder Nagar bungalow for Rs 64 crore
news.para: Shah has paid Rs 2.56 crore stamp duty for the registration of the property. According to documents accessed by CRE Matrix, a real estate data analytics firm, Star hotel PVR Ltd has sold the bungalow and property has been registered on October 31.
